eureka_ml_insights.configs.model_configs module

Module containing config objects for the models used in the experiments.

This module includes config objects for various models, specifying parameters such as model names, keys, and endpoints. To use these configs, replace the placeholders with your own keys.json file, secret key names, and endpoint URLs where applicable. You can also add your custom models by following the same pattern as the existing configs.
